definitions.definition: A newcomer , someone new to something.
examples: He was a newbie to chemistry.

definitions.definition: A new user or participant ; someone who is extremely new and inexperienced (to a game or activity). A beginner.
Anything recently introduced into a setting, especially something that replaces an older version.

main_definition: ( slang ) A newcomer , someone new to something. [from 20th c.]
